titles.title: An original resolution to authorize expenditures for the Committee on Energy and Natural Resources for the period March 1, 1993, through February 28, 1995.

calendar.text: Committee on Energy and Natural Resources ordered to be reported an original measure.

action.text: Committee on Energy and Natural Resources. Original measure reported to Senate by Senator Johnston. Without written report.
Referred to the Committee on Rules.

calendar.text: Committee on Rules. Provisions of measure incorporated into measure S.RES. 71 ordered to be reported.

bill.summary: 1/27/1993--Introduced. Authorizes expenditures by the Senate Committee on Energy and Natural Resources for the 103d Congress.
